{
  "video_id": "g-Uvy6pvLA4",
  "title": "Luke Syson: How I learned to stop worrying and love \"useless\" art",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12489.0,
      "end_time": 15458.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, I have to say there was no problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15458.0,
      "end_time": 19516.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, I knew exactly  what an icon looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19516.0,
      "end_time": 21871.0,
      "text": "It looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21871.0,
      "end_time": 24700.0,
      "text": "Everybody&#39;s icon, but also the default position"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24700.0,
      "end_time": 28523.0,
      "text": "of a curator of Italian Renaissance  paintings, which I was then."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28523.0,
      "end_time": 32215.0,
      "text": "And in a way, this is also another default selection."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32215.000000000004,
      "end_time": 36762.0,
      "text": "Leonardo da Vinci&#39;s exquisitely soulful image"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36762.0,
      "end_time": 38620.0,
      "text": "of the \"Lady with an Ermine.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38620.0,
      "end_time": 40605.0,
      "text": "And I use that word, soulful, deliberately."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40605.0,
      "end_time": 42988.0,
      "text": "Or then there&#39;s this, or rather these:"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42988.0,
      "end_time": 45641.0,
      "text": "the two versions of Leonardo&#39;s \"Virgin of the Rocks\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45642.0,
      "end_time": 49918.0,
      "text": "that were about to come together  in London for the very first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49918.0,
      "end_time": 54102.0,
      "text": "In the exhibition that I was then in  the absolute throes of organizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54102.0,
      "end_time": 57538.0,
      "text": "I was literally up to my eyes in Leonardo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57539.0,
      "end_time": 59357.0,
      "text": "and I had been for three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59357.0,
      "end_time": 63779.0,
      "text": "So, he was occupying every part of my brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63779.0,
      "end_time": 66620.0,
      "text": "Leonardo had taught me, during that three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66620.0,
      "end_time": 68468.0,
      "text": "about what a picture can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68468.0,
      "end_time": 73786.0,
      "text": "About taking you from your own  material world into a spiritual world."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73786.0,
      "end_time": 76677.0,
      "text": "He said, actually, that he believed  the job of the painter"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76677.0,
      "end_time": 81128.0,
      "text": "was to paint everything that was visible  and invisible in the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81128.0,
      "end_time": 85125.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a huge task. And yet,  somehow he achieves it."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85125.0,
      "end_time": 87896.0,
      "text": "He shows us, I think, the human soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87896.0,
      "end_time": 92342.0,
      "text": "He shows us the capacity of ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92342.0,
      "end_time": 95770.0,
      "text": "to move into a spiritual realm."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 95770.0,
      "end_time": 100298.0,
      "text": "To see a vision of the universe that&#39;s  more perfect than our own."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100298.0,
      "end_time": 103874.0,
      "text": "To see God&#39;s own plan, in some sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103874.0,
      "end_time": 107945.0,
      "text": "So this, in a sense, was really  what I believed an icon was."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107945.0,
      "end_time": 111803.0,
      "text": "At about that time, I started talking to Tom Campbell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111803.0,
      "end_time": 114354.0,
      "text": "director here of the Metropolitan Museum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114354.0,
      "end_time": 117678.0,
      "text": "about what my next move might be."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117678.0,
      "end_time": 120449.0,
      "text": "The move, in fact, back to an earlier life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 120449.0,
      "end_time": 122407.0,
      "text": "one I&#39;d begun at the British Museum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122407.0,
      "end_time": 124926.0,
      "text": "back to the world of three dimensions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124926.0,
      "end_time": 127158.0,
      "text": "of sculpture and of decorative arts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127158.0,
      "end_time": 131376.0,
      "text": "to take over the department of European sculpture  and decorative arts, here at the Met."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131376.0,
      "end_time": 132816.0,
      "text": "But it was an incredibly busy time."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132816.0,
      "end_time": 136223.0,
      "text": "All the conversations were done  at very peculiar times of the day --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 136223.0,
      "end_time": 139136.0,
      "text": "over the phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139136.0,
      "end_time": 141200.0,
      "text": "In the end, I accepted the job"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 141200.0,
      "end_time": 142572.0,
      "text": "without actually having been here."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142573.0,
      "end_time": 145125.0,
      "text": "Again, I&#39;d been there a couple of years before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145125.0,
      "end_time": 147637.0,
      "text": "but on that particular visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147637.0,
      "end_time": 151729.0,
      "text": "So, it was just before the time that  the Leonardo show was due to open"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151729.0,
      "end_time": 155751.0,
      "text": "when I finally made it back to the Met, to New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155751.0,
      "end_time": 157207.0,
      "text": "to see my new domain."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157207.0,
      "end_time": 161150.0,
      "text": "To see what European sculpture  and decorative arts looked like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161150.0,
      "end_time": 165941.0,
      "text": "beyond those Renaissance collections  with which I was so already familiar."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165941.0,
      "end_time": 168938.0,
      "text": "And I thought, on that very first day,  I better tour the galleries."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168938.0,
      "end_time": 170390.0,
      "text": "Fifty-seven of these galleries --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170390.0,
      "end_time": 175245.0,
      "text": "like 57 varieties of baked beans, I believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175246.0,
      "end_time": 181367.0,
      "text": "I walked through and I started in my comfort zone in the Italian Renaissance."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 181367.0,
      "end_time": 183287.0,
      "text": "And then I moved gradually around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 183288.0,
      "end_time": 186390.0,
      "text": "feeling a little lost sometimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 186390.0,
      "end_time": 189442.0,
      "text": "My head, also still full of the Leonardo exhibition"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189443.0,
      "end_time": 193465.0,
      "text": "that was about to open, and I came across this."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 193465.0,
      "end_time": 201395.0,
      "text": "And I thought to myself: What the hell have I done?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 201395.0,
      "end_time": 204748.0,
      "text": "There was absolutely no connection in my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 204748.0,
      "end_time": 207846.0,
      "text": "at all and, in fact, if there was any emotion going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 207847.0,
      "end_time": 210216.0,
      "text": "it was a kind of repulsion."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210216.0,
      "end_time": 213454.0,
      "text": "This object felt utterly and completely alien."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213454.0,
      "end_time": 218917.0,
      "text": "Silly at a level that I hadn&#39;t yet  understood silliness to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 218917.0,
      "end_time": 221116.0,
      "text": "And then it was made worse --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 221116.0,
      "end_time": 222961.0,
      "text": "there were two of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222961.0,
      "end_time": 226100.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 226100.0,
      "end_time": 229670.0,
      "text": "So, I started thinking about why it was, in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 229670.0,
      "end_time": 231523.0,
      "text": "that I disliked this object so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 231523.0,
      "end_time": 235329.0,
      "text": "What was the anatomy of my distaste?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235329.0,
      "end_time": 238797.0,
      "text": "Well, so much gold, so vulgar."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 238797.0,
      "end_time": 242651.0,
      "text": "You know, so nouveau riche, frankly."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 242651.0,
      "end_time": 245564.0,
      "text": "Leonardo himself had preached  against the use of gold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245564.0,
      "end_time": 248999.0,
      "text": "so it was absolutely anathema at that moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 248999.0,
      "end_time": 254427.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s little pretty sprigs  of flowers everywhere. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 254427.0,
      "end_time": 257945.0,
      "text": "And finally, that pink. That damned pink."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 257946.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260842.00000000003,
      "text": "It&#39;s such an extraordinarily artificial color."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 260841.0,
      "end_time": 264370.0,
      "text": "I mean, it&#39;s a color that I can&#39;t think of  anything that you actually see in nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264370.0,
      "end_time": 267458.0,
      "text": "that looks that shade."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267458.0,
      "end_time": 271198.0,
      "text": "The object even has its own tutu. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 271198.0,
      "end_time": 273558.0,
      "text": "This little flouncy, spangly, bottomy bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273558.0,
      "end_time": 275593.0,
      "text": "that sits at the bottom of the vase."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 275593.0,
      "end_time": 277966.0,
      "text": "It reminded me, in an odd kind of way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 277966.0,
      "end_time": 280650.0,
      "text": "of my niece&#39;s fifth birthday party."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 280650.0,
      "end_time": 284587.0,
      "text": "Where all the little girls would come  either as a princess or a fairy."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 284587.0,
      "end_time": 286467.0,
      "text": "There was one who would come as a fairy princess."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 286468.0,
      "end_time": 288890.0,
      "text": "You should have seen the looks."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 288890.0,
      "end_time": 290582.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 290583.0,
      "end_time": 293925.0,
      "text": "And I realize that this object was in my mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 293925.0,
      "end_time": 296865.0,
      "text": "born from the same mind, from the same womb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 296865.0,
      "end_time": 302890.0,
      "text": "practically, as Barbie Ballerina. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 302890.0,
      "end_time": 305611.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s the elephants. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 305611.0,
      "end_time": 307757.0,
      "text": "Those extraordinary elephants"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 307757.0,
      "end_time": 310481.0,
      "text": "with their little, sort of strange, sinister expressions"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 310481.0,
      "end_time": 315778.0,
      "text": "and Greta Garbo eyelashes, with  these golden tusks and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 315778.0,
      "end_time": 317554.0,
      "text": "I realized this was an elephant that had"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 317554.0,
      "end_time": 323287.0,
      "text": "absolutely nothing to do with a majestic  march across the Serengeti."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 323287.0,
      "end_time": 328782.0,
      "text": "It was a Dumbo nightmare. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 328782.0,
      "end_time": 331628.0,
      "text": "But something more profound  was happening as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 331628.0,
      "end_time": 333560.0,
      "text": "These objects, it seemed to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 333570.0,
      "end_time": 337366.0,
      "text": "were quintessentially the kind that I  and my liberal left friends in London"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 337366.0,
      "end_time": 339901.0,
      "text": "had always seen as summing up"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 339901.0,
      "end_time": 342740.0,
      "text": "something deplorable about the French aristocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 342740.0,
      "end_time": 344912.0,
      "text": "in the 18th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 344912.0,
      "end_time": 347700.0,
      "text": "The label had told me that these pieces were made"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 347701.0,
      "end_time": 350412.0,
      "text": "by the Sèvres Manufactory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 350412.0,
      "end_time": 353637.0,
      "text": "made of porcelain in the late 1750s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 353637.0,
      "end_time": 356768.0,
      "text": "and designed by a designer called  Jean-Claude Duplessis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 356768.0,
      "end_time": 358964.0,
      "text": "actually somebody of extraordinary distinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 358964.0,
      "end_time": 361441.0,
      "text": "as I later learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 361441.0,
      "end_time": 366248.0,
      "text": "But for me, they summed up a kind of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 366249.0,
      "end_time": 369663.0,
      "text": "that sort of sheer uselessness of the aristocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 369663.0,
      "end_time": 373136.0,
      "text": "in the 18th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 373136.0,
      "end_time": 375602.0,
      "text": "I and my colleagues had always thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 375602.0,
      "end_time": 378558.0,
      "text": "that these objects, in way, summed up the idea of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 378558.0,
      "end_time": 380921.0,
      "text": "you know -- no wonder there was a revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 380922.0,
      "end_time": 385465.0,
      "text": "Or, indeed, thank God there was a revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 385465.0,
      "end_time": 387224.0,
      "text": "There was a sort of idea really, that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 387224.0,
      "end_time": 389897.0,
      "text": "if you owned a vase like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 389897.0,
      "end_time": 393621.0,
      "text": "then there was really only one fate possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 393621.0,
      "end_time": 397685.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 397685.0,
      "end_time": 402349.0,
      "text": "So, there I was -- in a sort of paroxysm of horror."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 402349.0,
      "end_time": 406308.0,
      "text": "But I took the job and I went  on looking at these vases."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 406309.0,
      "end_time": 409840.0,
      "text": "I sort of had to because they&#39;re  on a through route in the Met."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 409840.0,
      "end_time": 412472.0,
      "text": "So, almost anywhere I went, there they were."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 412472.0,
      "end_time": 415241.0,
      "text": "They had this kind of odd sort of fascination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 415241.0,
      "end_time": 418258.0,
      "text": "like a car accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 418259.0,
      "end_time": 420983.0,
      "text": "Where I couldn&#39;t stop looking."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 420983.0,
      "end_time": 423205.0,
      "text": "And as I did so, I started thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 423205.0,
      "end_time": 427733.0,
      "text": "Well, what are we actually looking at here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 427733.0,
      "end_time": 431640.0,
      "text": "And what I started with was understanding this"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 431640.0,
      "end_time": 434616.0,
      "text": "as really a supreme piece of design."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 434616.0,
      "end_time": 435712.0,
      "text": "It took me a little time."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 435713.0,
      "end_time": 437151.0,
      "text": "But, that tutu for example --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 437151.0,
      "end_time": 440273.0,
      "text": "actually, this is a piece that  does dance in its own way."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 440273.0,
      "end_time": 441915.0,
      "text": "It has an extraordinary lightness"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 441915.0,
      "end_time": 444430.0,
      "text": "and yet, it is also amazing balanced."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 444430.0,
      "end_time": 447905.0,
      "text": "It has these kinds of sculptural ingredients."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 447905.0,
      "end_time": 449544.0,
      "text": "And then the play between --"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 449544.0,
      "end_time": 454156.0,
      "text": "actually really quite carefully disposed  color and gilding, and the sculptural surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 454156.0,
      "end_time": 456431.0,
      "text": "is really rather remarkable."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 456431.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "And then I realized that this piece went into the kiln"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 459261.0,
      "end_time": 462651.0,
      "text": "four times, at least four times  in order to arrive at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 462651.0,
      "end_time": 465705.0,
      "text": "How many moments for accident can you think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 465705.0,
      "end_time": 467209.0,
      "text": "that could have happened to this piece?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 467209.0,
      "end_time": 469771.0,
      "text": "And then remember, not just one, but two."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 469771.0,
      "end_time": 474360.0,
      "text": "So he&#39;s having to arrive at two exactly matched"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 474360.0,
      "end_time": 476548.0,
      "text": "vases of this kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 476548.0,
      "end_time": 477954.0,
      "text": "And then this question of uselessness."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 477954.0,
      "end_time": 482913.0,
      "text": "Well actually, the end of the trunks  were originally candle holders."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 482913.0,
      "end_time": 486663.0,
      "text": "So what you would have had  were candles on either side."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 486663.0,
      "end_time": 489219.0,
      "text": "Imagine that effect of candlelight on that surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 489219.0,
      "end_time": 491951.0,
      "text": "On the slightly uneven pink, on the beautiful gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 491951.0,
      "end_time": 494697.0,
      "text": "It would have glittered in an interior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 494697.0,
      "end_time": 497779.0,
      "text": "a little like a little firework."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 497779.0,
      "end_time": 501431.0,
      "text": "And at that point, actually,  a firework went off in my brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 501431.0,
      "end_time": 504265.0,
      "text": "Somebody reminded me that, that word &#39;fancy&#39; --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 504266.0,
      "end_time": 507376.0,
      "text": "which in a sense for me, encapsulated this object --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 507376.0,
      "end_time": 511421.0,
      "text": "actually comes from the same  root as the word &#39;fantasy.&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 511422.0,
      "end_time": 514380.0,
      "text": "And that what this object was just as much in a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 514380.0,
      "end_time": 516490.0,
      "text": "in its own way, as a Leonardo da Vinci painting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 516490.0,
      "end_time": 518697.0,
      "text": "is a portal to somewhere else."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 518697.0,
      "end_time": 522892.0,
      "text": "This is an object of the imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 522892.00000000006,
      "end_time": 529701.0,
      "text": "If you think about the mad 18th-century  operas of the time -- set in the Orient."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 529721.0,
      "end_time": 536200.0,
      "text": "If you think about divans and perhaps even  opium-induced visions of pink elephants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 536200.0,
      "end_time": 539501.0,
      "text": "then at that point, this object starts to make sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 539501.0,
      "end_time": 543557.0,
      "text": "This is an object which is all about escapism."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 543557.0,
      "end_time": 546754.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about an escapism that happens --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 546754.0,
      "end_time": 548775.0,
      "text": "that the aristocracy in France sought"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 548775.0,
      "end_time": 550560.0,
      "text": "very deliberately"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 550561.0,
      "end_time": 555129.0,
      "text": "to distinguish themselves from ordinary people."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 555129.0,
      "end_time": 557930.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not an escapism that"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 557930.0,
      "end_time": 560959.0,
      "text": "we feel particularly happy with today, however."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 560960.0,
      "end_time": 563945.0,
      "text": "And again, going on thinking about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 563945.0,
      "end_time": 567119.0,
      "text": "I realize that in a way we&#39;re all victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 567119.0,
      "end_time": 569130.0,
      "text": "of a certain kind of tyranny"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 569130.0,
      "end_time": 571151.0,
      "text": "of the triumph of modernism"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 571151.0,
      "end_time": 573877.0,
      "text": "whereby form and function in an object"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 573877.0,
      "end_time": 577281.0,
      "text": "have to follow one another, or are deemed to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 577282.0,
      "end_time": 580246.0,
      "text": "And the extraneous ornament is seen as really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 580246.0,
      "end_time": 583266.0,
      "text": "essentially, criminal."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 583266.0,
      "end_time": 586416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a triumph, in a way, of bourgeois values rather than aristocratic ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 586417.0,
      "end_time": 588240.0,
      "text": "And that seems fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 588240.0,
      "end_time": 595697.0,
      "text": "Except for the fact that it becomes a kind of  sequestration of imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 595697.0,
      "end_time": 598387.0,
      "text": "So just as in the 20th century, so many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 598387.0,
      "end_time": 600375.0,
      "text": "had the idea that their faith"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 600375.0,
      "end_time": 603570.0,
      "text": "took place on the Sabbath day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 603570.0,
      "end_time": 604431.0,
      "text": "and the rest of their lives --"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 604431.0,
      "end_time": 608409.0,
      "text": "their lives of washing machines and orthodontics --"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 608409.0,
      "end_time": 610441.0,
      "text": "took place on another day."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 610441.0,
      "end_time": 614209.0,
      "text": "Then, I think we&#39;ve started doing the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 614209.0,
      "end_time": 617540.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve allowed ourselves to"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 617541.0,
      "end_time": 619898.0,
      "text": "lead our fantasy lives in front of screens."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 619898.0,
      "end_time": 623880.0,
      "text": "In the dark of the cinema, with the television in the corner of the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 623880.0,
      "end_time": 627958.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve eliminated, in a sense, that constant"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 627958.0,
      "end_time": 632886.0,
      "text": "of the imagination that these vases  represented in people&#39;s lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 632886.0,
      "end_time": 636921.0,
      "text": "So maybe it&#39;s time we got this back a little."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 636922.0,
      "end_time": 639272.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s beginning to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 639272.0,
      "end_time": 640538.0,
      "text": "In London, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 640538.0,
      "end_time": 642687.0,
      "text": "with these extraordinary buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 642687.0,
      "end_time": 645678.0,
      "text": "that have been appearing over the last few years."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 645678.0,
      "end_time": 648810.0,
      "text": "Redolent, in a sense, of science fiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 648810.0,
      "end_time": 650195.0,
      "text": "turning London into a kind of fantasy playground."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 650195.0,
      "end_time": 655490.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually amazing to look out of  a high building nowadays there."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 655490.0,
      "end_time": 656853.0,
      "text": "But even then, there&#39;s a resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 656853.0,
      "end_time": 661189.0,
      "text": "London has called these buildings the  Gherkin, the Shard, the Walkie Talkie --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 661189.0,
      "end_time": 664493.0,
      "text": "bringing these soaring buildings down to Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 664494.0,
      "end_time": 668574.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an idea that we don&#39;t want these"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 668574.0,
      "end_time": 673435.0,
      "text": "anxious-making, imaginative journeys  to happen in our daily lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 673435.0,
      "end_time": 676703.0,
      "text": "I feel lucky in a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 676703.0,
      "end_time": 679251.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve encountered this object."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 679251.0,
      "end_time": 681692.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 681692.0,
      "end_time": 684994.0,
      "text": "I found him on the Internet when  I was looking up a reference."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 684994.0,
      "end_time": 687888.0,
      "text": "And there he was."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 687888.0,
      "end_time": 691202.0,
      "text": "And unlike the pink elephant vase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 691202.0,
      "end_time": 693175.0,
      "text": "this was a kind of love at first sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 693175.0,
      "end_time": 696310.0,
      "text": "In fact, reader, I married him. I bought him."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 696310.0,
      "end_time": 699895.0,
      "text": "And he now adorns my office."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 699895.0,
      "end_time": 703436.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a Staffordshire figure made  in the middle of the 19th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 703436.0,
      "end_time": 708242.0,
      "text": "He represents the actor, Edmund Kean,  playing Shakespeare&#39;s Richard III."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 708242.0,
      "end_time": 710694.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s based, actually, on a more  elevated piece of porcelain."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 710695.0,
      "end_time": 712849.0,
      "text": "So I loved, on an art historical level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 712849.0,
      "end_time": 717509.0,
      "text": "I loved that layered quality that he has."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 717509.0,
      "end_time": 720200.0,
      "text": "But more than that, I love him."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 720200.0,
      "end_time": 721680.0,
      "text": "In a way that I think would have been impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 721680.0,
      "end_time": 724291.0,
      "text": "without the pink Sèvres vase in my Leonardo days."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 724292.0,
      "end_time": 727509.0,
      "text": "I love his orange and pink breeches."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 727509.0,
      "end_time": 730259.0,
      "text": "I love the fact that he seems to be going off to war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 730259.0,
      "end_time": 734691.0,
      "text": "having just finished the washing up. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 734691.0,
      "end_time": 737168.0,
      "text": "He seems also to have forgotten his sword."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 737168.0,
      "end_time": 739787.0,
      "text": "I love his pink little cheeks, his munchkin energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 739787.0,
      "end_time": 742978.0,
      "text": "In a way, he&#39;s become my sort of alter ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 742978.0,
      "end_time": 745279.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s, I hope, a little bit dignified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 745279.0,
      "end_time": 750453.0,
      "text": "but mostly rather vulgar. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 750453.0,
      "end_time": 753670.0,
      "text": "And energetic, I hope, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 753671.0,
      "end_time": 758826.0,
      "text": "I let him into my life because the Sèvres pink elephant vase allowed me to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 758826.0,
      "end_time": 760394.0,
      "text": "And before that Leonardo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 760394.0,
      "end_time": 765500.0,
      "text": "I understood that this object could become  part of a journey for me every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 765500.0,
      "end_time": 768245.0,
      "text": "sitting in my office."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 768245.0,
      "end_time": 771234.0,
      "text": "I really hope that others, all of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 771234.0,
      "end_time": 772809.0,
      "text": "visiting objects in the museum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 772809.0,
      "end_time": 775262.0,
      "text": "and taking them home and  finding them for yourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 775263.0,
      "end_time": 779577.0,
      "text": "will allow those objects to flourish  in your imaginative lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 779577.0,
      "end_time": 781130.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 781130.0,
      "end_time": 785130.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}